resources.string:
Instructions:
1.Press the Start button to begin the run. 
(this will start the stopwatch)
2.Press the stop button to end this running session.
Instructions:\nEnter the number of reps you completed and press Save when you are done.
Instructions:\nClick on the respective picture below (an image of a NAPFA test item) to navigate to the respective NAPFA test item submit result page.

Instructions:
1.Select whether you wish to review results of all NAPFA test results (or specify the number of NAPFA test results to show).
2. Click on Review and the results will be populated on the table below.
Show the specified no. of result\n(Choose 0 to show all results for the test station).
